# ==============================================================================
# STEP-BY-STEP PUBLISHING CONFIGURATION
# 
# By default, this file ignores all the contents inside the Skills folders so 
# you don't accidentally push everything at once.
#
# HOW TO USE:
# To push a specific sub-category to GitHub, simply UNCOMMENT (remove the `#`) 
# from the line corresponding to the folder you want to push.
#
# Example: To push "Agents & LLMs", change:
# # !/AI-ML & Data Science Skills/Agents & LLMs/
# to:
# !/AI-ML & Data Science Skills/Agents & LLMs/
# ==============================================================================

# 1. Ignore all contents inside the Category folders
/* Skills/*

# 2. Whitelist (Allow) specific sub-categories. UNCOMMENT to push!

# --- AI-ML & Data Science Skills ---
!/AI-ML & Data Science Skills/Agents & LLMs/
!/AI-ML & Data Science Skills/Data Science & Analytics/
!/AI-ML & Data Science Skills/Machine Learning/

# --- Business & Marketing Skills ---
!/Business & Marketing Skills/Business & Sales/
!/Business & Marketing Skills/Marketing & SEO/
!/Business & Marketing Skills/Product Management/

# --- Development & Engineering Skills ---
!/Development & Engineering Skills/Backend & APIs/
!/Development & Engineering Skills/General Coding & Architecture/
!/Development & Engineering Skills/Mobile Development/
# !/Development & Engineering Skills/Web Development/

# --- Security & DevOps Skills ---
# !/Security & DevOps Skills/Cyber Security/
# !/Security & DevOps Skills/DevOps & Infrastructure/

# --- System Design & UI-UX Skills ---
# !/System Design & UI-UX Skills/UX/

# --- Writing & Productivity Skills ---
# !/Writing & Productivity Skills/Productivity & Workflow/
# !/Writing & Productivity Skills/Writing & Content/

# ==============================================================================
# Standard Ignored Files (Node, OS files, etc.)
# ==============================================================================
node_modules/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.agents/
scratch/
